Class GlobalMincut.CutPhase

    GlobalMincut

    private class GlobalMincut.CutPhase
extends java.lang.Object
    This helper class represents the cut-of-the-phase. The cut-of-the-phase is a minimum s-t-cut in the current graph, where s and t are the two vertices added last in the phase.
